Interesting Plots
Customers This plot depicts the number of customers by state.

plot(customers)

Order Details This plot indicates the quantity of types of items across orders details.

plot(order_details)
## stat_bin: binwidth defaulted to range/30. Use 'binwidth = x' to adjust this.

Orders
This plot displays the types of items ordered by each customer over a period of time.

plot(orders)

Items This plot shows the price distribution of items across different artists.

plot(items)
